<HEADLINE>
Four dead, two missing as storm-blasted yacht race ends on grim
</HEADLINE>
note &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with rescue operation called off, new quote from race
spokesman, spokesman revising death count to four sted five, with
British sailor missing and presumed drowned; ADDS identity of
missing Australian sailor; raises number of boats withdrawing from
race to 70; inquiry launched; CORRECTS spelling of helicopter
pilot's name to Trimmer, sted Trimmor. &QL; 
