 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with troops clashing with kidnappers &QL; 

<TEXT>
	   SAN`A, Yemen (AP) _ Security forces clashed with the abductors
of 16 foreign tourists in Yemen Tuesday, an official said.
	   He said there were casualties but did not specify whether any of
the hostages were killed when the forces stormed the hideout of the
kidnappers and exchanged gunfire with them.
