<TEXT>
	   SAN`A, Yemen (AP) _ Security forces clashed with the abductors
of 16 foreign tourists in southern Yemen on Tuesday, an official
said. He said there were casualties in the fighting but did not
specify whether any of the hostages were killed.
	   The hostages, who were kidnapped Monday, include 12 Britons, two
Americans and two Australians.
