<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Yemen-Kidnapping, 2nd Ld-Writethru </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Security official: Three hostages killed in shootout
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; URGENT &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with report three hostages killed, CHANGES overline,
RESTORES byline. &QL; 
 &UR; By AHMAD AL-HAJ &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   SAN`A, Yemen (AP) _ Three Western tourists _ two of them from
Britain and an American _ were killed on Tuesday when Yemeni troops
clashed with their kidnappers, a Yemen security official said.
	   The two British men and an American woman died as the troops
stormed the hideout where they were being held in an attempt to
rescue them and 13 others, the official said. He spoke on customary
condition of anonymity.
