<HEADLINE>
Security official: Three hostages killed in shootout in Yemen
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; URGENT &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES with report three hostages killed, CHANGES overline,
RESTORES byline. &QL; 
 &UR; By AHMAD AL-HAJ &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   SAN`A, Yemen (AP) _ Three tourists _ two Britons and an American
_ were killed Tuesday when Yemeni troops clashed with their
kidnappers, a Yemeni security official said.
	   The two British men and one American woman died as the troops
stormed the kidnappers' hideout in an attempt to rescue the three
hostages and 13 others, the official said, speaking on customary
condition of anonymity.
