<HEADLINE>
Newspaper: Dugarry will join Juventus after New Year
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   MILAN, Italy (AP) _ Marseille striker Christophe Dugarry is
expected to sign with Juventus of Turin in time to start play just
after the start of the new year, Italy's Gazzetta dello Sport
reported Tuesday.
	   Juventus is expected to pay Marseille about dlrs 8.4 million.
