	   _5.5952 French francs, down from 5.6380
	   _1.8815 Dutch guilders, down from 1.8942
	   _1,652.10 Italian lire, down from 1,664.95
	   _1.5512 Canadian dollars, up from 1.5497
	   The British pound was quoted at dlrs 1.6832, up from dlrs
1.6730.
