</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: corrects that Man Utd goes third &QL; 

<TEXT>
	   LONDON (AP) _ Tore Andre Flo and Gianfranco Zola missed four
good chances as Chelsea squandered a chance to regain top place in
the Premier League from Aston Villa on Tuesday after a 0-0 tie with
Manchester United.
	   Flo had three opportunities in the first half while the
ever-dangerous Zola had two. The experienced Italian got round
