<HEADLINE>
Dollar higher against yen in Tokyo
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   TOKYO (AP) _ The U.S. dollar was trading at 115.70 yen on the
Tokyo foreign exchange market at 9 a.m. (0000 GMT) Wednesday, up
0.34 yen from its level of 115.36 yen as of 5 p.m. (0800 GMT)
Tuesday. 	   
