<DOCNO> APW19981229.1241 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 12/29/1998 20:06:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
w2153 &Cx1f; wstm-
r i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-Australia-DeadlyYacht     12-29 0809
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Australia-Deadly Yacht Race </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Inquiries to follow Australian race disaster
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: RECAPS previous. Also moved on sports wire &QL; 
 &UR; By TONY HARPER &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

