<HEADLINE>
NHL Glance, Sub-Standings
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; By The Associated Press &QC; 
 &UR; All Times EST &QC; 
 &UR; EASTERN CONFERENCE &QC; 
 &UR; Atlantic Division &QC; 
                   &Cx1f;  &UR; W    L    T  Pts    GF    GA
