</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   TOKYO (AP) _ The Nikkei Stock Average of 225 issues closed a
half-day session Wednesday, the year's last trading day, finishing
at 13,842.17 points, down 4.73 points, or 0.03 percent, from
Tuesday.
	   The Tokyo Stock Exchange will be closed through Jan. 3 for New
Year's holidays. The market will reopen Monday, Jan. 4. 	   
